OL,3,CSoggy start to June as record-breaking
OL,4,CUK heatwave gives way to thunderstorms
OL,6,FThere will be a soggy start to June in
OL,7,Fmany parts of the UK as record-
OL,8,Fbreaking temperatures give way to
OL,9,Fthunderstorms and cooler weather.
OL,11,FThe south and south east of England
OL,12,Fwill enjoy a continuation of the warm
OL,13,Fweather and sunshine this weekend,
OL,14,Fwhile downpours in other parts will
OL,15,Fput a dampen on the unseasonal hot
OL,16,Fspell, with outbreaks of rain, with
OL,17,Fshowers expected to be at their "most
OL,18,Ffrequent and heaviest" in northern and
OL,19,Fwestern areas on Sunday.
OL,26,@yD@aOUzD@VO]
