PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780171548
OL,3,CSoggy start to June as record-breaking
OL,4,CUK heatwave gives way to thunderstorms
OL,6,FHe said: "Particularly (during) the
OL,7,Fmiddle to second half of June, it
OL,8,Flooks like it starts settling down
OL,9,Fwith higher pressure a bit more
OL,10,Fdominant again, so an unsettled start
OL,11,Fto meteorological summer, but there
OL,12,Fare signs that it does settle down as
OL,13,Fthe month goes on."
OL,15,FEngland and Wales recorded the hottest
OL,16,Fdays in May on record on Tuesday.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@SO]
