OL,3,CSoggy start to June as record-breaking
OL,4,CUK heatwave gives way to thunderstorms
OL,6,FTemperatures soared to 35.1C in Kew
OL,7,FGardens, west London, while
OL,8,Ftemperatures in Cardiff's Bute Park
OL,9,Freached 32.9C, according to the Met
OL,10,FOffice.
OL,12,FCharlie Noble, 16, became the 12th
OL,13,Fperson to die in a water-related
OL,14,Fincident over the course of the
OL,15,Fheatwave when his body was recovered
OL,16,Fin Stirlingshire, Scotland, on
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
