PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780171548
OL,3,CSoggy start to June as record-breaking
OL,4,CUK heatwave gives way to thunderstorms
OL,6,FThere have been deaths in South
OL,7,FYorkshire, West Yorkshire, Cornwall,
OL,8,FHampshire, Warwickshire, Cheshire,
OL,9,FPembrokeshire, Lincolnshire and
OL,10,FLancashire.
OL,12,FThousands of people in Kent are
OL,13,Fexpected to face water issues this
OL,14,Fweekend as South East Water continues
OL,15,Fto grapple with its supply during the
OL,16,Fhot weather.
OL,18,FBusinesses have closed and residents
OL,19,Fhave been queuing up at water bottle
OL,20,Fstations since problems began amid the
OL,21,Fbank holiday weekend heat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
